      "writtenOn": "2026-01-21T18:46:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The error turned out to be a validation that the sdnrdb-init-job was doing on the version of mariadb - it was expecting an older version than is currently being used.  The sdnc-ansible-server depends on the sdnc-web server, so that same issue impacted both.\n\nWe changed our code to eliminate that check.  Unfortunately we have been struggling for the last few weeks with various compile issues on the LF Jenkins servers to get that fix built, but at long last, today we finally were able to get the new image built.\n\nAt long last, we finally have the new image built.  I\u0027ll be pushing an update shortly with the updated SDNC image version.",
